requirement:
During the roll-to-level segment, transition to the landing rollout segment when any of the following conditions are met, with a softened time limit set to 2 seconds.
1) The landing gear fully compressed signal is true for 12 consecutive frames;
2) The remote control ground contact signal is true;
3) The cumulative number of frames where the remote control signal status is abnormal reaches 75. Note, this condition only needs to be evaluated once.
